  "texts": [
    "Alzanin and Azmi [67] constructed datasets that consisted of 27,100 posts related to 177 events from different domains, where 88 of these events were considered non-rumors, while 89 were rumors.",
    "This dataset also includes some features from users and contents.",
    "During the COVID-19 pandemic, researchers were encouraged to construct datasets covering this topic [74] [76].",
    "Furthermore, [74] constructed a bilingual dataset that covers the Arabic and English languages.",
    "The dataset was collected from Twitter using keywords related to COVID-19."
  ]
}